What is the output of the following code?
```python
class Vehicle:
    def describe(self):
        return "Vehicle"

class Car(Vehicle):
    def describe(self):
        return super().describe() + " > Car"

class ElectricCar(Car):
    def describe(self):
        return super().describe() + " > ElectricCar"

ec = ElectricCar()
print(ec.describe())
```

